    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/4274e6a044e578860b352ec6e3344184.poster.avif?t=1771348223\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/4274e6a044e578860b352ec6e3344184.webm?t=1771348223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/4274e6a044e578860b352ec6e3344184.mp4?t=1771348223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Heavily inspired by old retro horror games, <strong><i>FLESH EVEREST</i></strong> mixes intense survival horror with slow-paced fps combat. Ammo is rare, enemies are tough, and each bullet counts. Built within a massive living organism, the <i>Flesh Everest Nature Attraction</i> is a one-of-a-kind facility that's open to the public and scientists alike. It seems however, that some cataclysmic event is occurring. Play as a police officer attempting to save those trapped below the flesh's surface.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Intense Gory Combat</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/473081a1665ec76bc0ccbd603e6a8dbf.poster.avif?t=1771348223\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/473081a1665ec76bc0ccbd603e6a8dbf.webm?t=1771348223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/473081a1665ec76bc0ccbd603e6a8dbf.mp4?t=1771348223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Face <strong>numerous different flesh entities with varying levels of threat.</strong> Some may be docile while others are highly aggressive.<br></li><li>Some entities, while slow, are <strong>unkillable</strong> and force the player to flee.<br></li><li>Contains minimal save points with a permadeath option.<br></li><li><strong>Physics based</strong> ragdolls and props.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Randomized Horror</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/e442e773a40983cb84d277a105a1ad72.poster.avif?t=1771348223\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/e442e773a40983cb84d277a105a1ad72.webm?t=1771348223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/e442e773a40983cb84d277a105a1ad72.mp4?t=1771348223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>No two playthroughs will ever be the same.<br></li><li>All weapons, ammo, and entities are <strong>fully randomized</strong>.<br></li><li>The facility is built from a mix of randomized rooms and corridors with non-random landmarks.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Scavenge for Survival</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/a21efe375cd1d3b4a992ac715cde16f8.poster.avif?t=1771348223\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/a21efe375cd1d3b4a992ac715cde16f8.webm?t=1771348223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/a21efe375cd1d3b4a992ac715cde16f8.mp4?t=1771348223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over <strong>12 different weapons</strong> to discover.<br></li><li>Each weapon has its own rarity directly related to its spawn chance.<br></li><li>Ammo is scarce and <strong>each shot counts.</strong><br></li><li>There are <strong>4 different ammo types</strong> with varying spawn chances.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Perk System</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/82858227424a598ca05476711522aa7d.poster.avif?t=1771348223\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/82858227424a598ca05476711522aa7d.webm?t=1771348223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/82858227424a598ca05476711522aa7d.mp4?t=1771348223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Game flow can be adjusted with perks.<br></li><li>Choose from <strong>8 different perks</strong>, each with its own unique ability.<br></li><li>Perks can be adjusted periodically during a playthrough.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NPC Storylines</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/b59dc7db7773d0700844060922a0a965.poster.avif?t=1771348223\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/b59dc7db7773d0700844060922a0a965.webm?t=1771348223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/b59dc7db7773d0700844060922a0a965.mp4?t=1771348223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Encounter and speak with multiple npcs within the facility.<br></li><li>Some npcs have <strong>quests and storylines</strong> associated with them.<br></li><li>An NPC may or may not be real.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Endings and Secrets</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/09c0571c3ecd33145f8d312d6ac7b7a1.poster.avif?t=1771348223\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/09c0571c3ecd33145f8d312d6ac7b7a1.webm?t=1771348223\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019010/extras/09c0571c3ecd33145f8d312d6ac7b7a1.mp4?t=1771348223\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Endings change based on the player's actions.<br></li><li>There are <strong>over 3 different endings</strong> to experience.<br></li><li>Numerous secrets are hidden throughout the facility.</li></ul>",
